1	Un JUNTOS productivo	A Productive JUNTOS	web	http://www.lampadia.com/opiniones/jaime-de-althaus/un-juntos-productivo/	<p>El presidente Ollanta Humala pone cada vez m&aacute;s &eacute;nfasis en que hay que crecer para incluir. Pero, por alguna extra&ntilde;a raz&oacute;n, hay una conspiraci&oacute;n t&aacute;cita contra un programa que le permitir&iacute;a no solo incluir, sino incluir creciendo, un programa de inclusi&oacute;n productiva que podr&iacute;a ser el instrumento m&aacute;s potente imaginable para producir la revoluci&oacute;n redistributiva que &eacute;l quisiera. Me refiero a Sierra Productiva, que instala reservorios familiares, riego por aspersi&oacute;n y otras tecnolog&iacute;as en las chacras de los m&aacute;s pobres, que salen as&iacute; de la pobreza en menos de un a&ntilde;o.</p>	<p>President Ollanta Humala puts more and more emphasis on the need to grow to include. But, for some strange reason, there is a tacit conspiracy against a program that would allow him not only to include, but to include growing, a program of productive inclusion that could be the most powerful instrument imaginable to produce the redistributive revolution that he wanted. I am referring to Sierra Productiva, which installs family reservoirs, sprinkler irrigation and other technologies in the farms of the poorest, who thus escape poverty in less than a year.</p>	2022-12-12 17:14:12.205335+00	2022-12-12 17:14:12.205352+00	1	114	1	22
2	Salto tecnológico para dejar atrás el hambre en el campo	Technological leap to leave hunger behind in the countryside	web	http://archivo.elcomercio.pe/economia/negocios/salto-tecnologico-dejar-atras-hambre-campo_1-noticia-296462	<p>A trav&eacute;s del proyecto Mi Chacra Productiva, los campesinos m&aacute;s pobres de Huancavelica recibir&aacute;n un apoyo del Estado para, de una vez, lograr mantenerse por s&iacute; solos.</p>	<p>Through the Mi Chacra Productiva project, the poorest peasants of Huancavelica will receive support from the State so that, once and for all, they will be able to support themselves.</p>	2022-12-12 17:20:57.764981+00	2022-12-12 17:20:57.764998+00	2	115	1	22
3	Sierra Productiva será programa estratégico del Ceplan	Sierra Productiva will be Ceplan&#39;s strategic program	web	https://archivo.gestion.pe/noticia/365684/sierra-productiva-programa-estrategico-ceplan	<p>Afirm&oacute; el presidente del Centro Nacional de Planeamiento Estrat&eacute;gico, Agust&iacute;n Haya de la Torre.</p>	<p>Affirmed the president of the National Center for Strategic Planning, Agust&iacute;n Haya de la Torre.</p>	2022-12-12 17:22:29.116031+00	2022-12-12 17:22:29.116047+00	3	118	1	22
4	Profundizarán lucha contra desnutrición e impulsarán programa Sierra Productiva	The government will deepen the fight against malnutrition and boost the Sierra Productiva program	web	https://andina.pe/agencia/noticia.aspx?id=214448	<p>El Ministerio de la Mujer y Desarrollo Social (Mimdes) viene dise&ntilde;ando una propuesta en el marco del Plan Anticrisis, que comprende dos temas: por un lado, profundizar la lucha contra la desnutrici&oacute;n, y por otro lado, impulsar el programa denominado Sierra Productiva, que tiene un conjunto de tecnolog&iacute;as para campesinos.</p>	<p>The Ministry of Women and Social Development (Mimdes) has been designing a proposal within the framework of the Anti-Crisis Plan, which includes two themes: on the one hand, deepening the fight against malnutrition, and on the other hand, promoting the program called Sierra Productiva, which has a set of technologies for farmers.</p>	2022-12-12 17:24:36.778202+00	2022-12-12 17:24:36.778217+00	4	120	1	22
5	Programa peruano Sierra Productiva obtuvo segundo lugar de World Challenge 2010	Peruvian Sierra Productiva program won second place in World Challenge 2010	web	https://andina.pe/agencia/noticia.aspx?id=333552	<p>El programa peruano Sierra Productiva obtuvo el segundo lugar en la sexta edici&oacute;n del World Challenge (Desaf&iacute;o Mundial), organizado por la cadena informativa BBC de Londres y la revista Newsweek, que esta vez recibi&oacute; 800 candidaturas de m&aacute;s de 70 pa&iacute;ses.</p>	<p>The Peruvian program Sierra Productiva won second place in the sixth edition of the World Challenge, organized by the BBC in London and Newsweek magazine, which this time received 800 nominations from more than 70 countries.</p>	2022-12-12 17:25:44.246116+00	2022-12-12 17:25:44.246133+00	4	121	1	22
